		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Growing up in Ontario, Canada, all of our school computers were <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Unisys_ICON" class="postlink">Unisys ICON</a> systems up to a depressingly late date. The Wikipedia article says that it &quot;disappeared&quot; after the late 80s, but that's not true - I remember programming in Logo on it in Grade 5, and that was the late 90s!<br /><br />For whatever reason at my school someone had made the login screen a charmingly amateurish vector illustration of Samus blasting a metroid. I wish I knew more about that or had a picture or anything.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
